, 
<figureCitation id="A59C2A165201FF8EFCE2FF2EFC52F9A1" box="[886,923,1612,1636]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1868,1891]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,841,1847]" captionTargetId="figure-385@3.[151,1436,841,1847]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 3. Ventral view of head in: (A) Yaoshania pachychilus, KIZ 200241655, 51.2 mm SL, (B) Erromyzon kalotaenia, KIZ 200304314, 47.8 mm SL, (C) E. sinensis KIZ 200304306, 39.8 mm SL, and (D) E. yangi, KIZ 200304423, 42.8 SL. ell, enlarged lip lamina; fl, flesh lobe; lj, lower jaw; ll, lower lip; mb, maxillary barbel; rb, rostral barbels; rf, rostral fold; rg, rostral groove; sp, small papilla; uj, upper jaw; ul, upper lip." pageId="1" pageNumber="174">3A</figureCitation>
